---
title: Saucy Beef Meatball Subs with Mozzarella
description: The classic Italian meatball sub is an incredibly popular sandwich for a multitude of great reasons. It’s basically everything that’s good and right in the world, tucked into a toasty baguette. This one’s exceptionally easy to get to the table (or into a lunchbox). Is 15 minutes fast enough for you? We’ll take the opportunity to shout out our fully cooked meatballs—a delicious shortcut to a speedy meal! Add lots of marinara sauce and melty mozzarella, and you’ve got yourself a sub-lime lunch idea!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64ee40810e79eb0332e2e50c-185f3de1.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/64ee40810e79eb0332e2e50c.pdf
time required: 15m
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/saucy-beef-meatball-subs-64ee40810e79eb0332e2e50c
course: main course
